@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_wdvbli(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.abs((wp.abs(v1 + 0.93) + v1))
    tmp = 0.21
    v0 = ((0.57 - (v0 + 0.72 - v0 + 0.50)) + (wp.sin(tmp + 0.26) * (v2 + 0.05 - v0 + 0.31)))
    data[tid] = v0
